300
01:02:48.346 --> 01:02:52.182
<i>in such close proximity with Hal?</i>

301
01:02:52.183 --> 01:02:54.392
<i>It's like what you said earlier.</i>

302
01:02:54.393 --> 01:02:56.770
<i>He's just like
