552
01:42:50.829 --> 01:42:53.205
Hal, I won't argue with you anymore.

553
01:42:53.206 --> 01:42:55.041
Open the doors.

554
01:42:55.042 --> 01:42:56.751
<i>Dave...</i>

555
01:42:56.752 --> 01:43:01.752
