578
01:51:45.280 --> 01:51:50.280
<i>and I want to help you.</i>

579
01:51:52.036 --> 01:51:54.538
<i>Dave...</i>

580
01:51:54.539 --> 01:51:55.083
<i>stop.</i>

581
01:52:00.170 --> 01:52:05.170
<i>Stop, will you?</i>

